 still common. This surname is also found in England."]},{"name":"Waldren","meanings":["English: variant of   Waldron  ."]},{"name":"Waldrum","meanings":["English: variant of   Waldron  ."]},{"name":"Walrond","meanings":["English (Somerset and Devon): of Normin origin, a variant of   Waldron  ."]}]},{"name":"John","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["As a boy's name this represents a revival of Middle English <i>Jan</i>, a by‐form of   John  , or an adoption of the common European form with this spelling. As a girl's name it is a short form of names such as   Janet   and   Janice ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"John Waldron was born in 1410. He had at least 1 son with Elizabeth Waldron. He died in 1510, at the age of 100."},"et":{"1410–1510":"1410–1510","1410–1500":"1410–1500","1471–1536":"1471–1536","1536":"1536","1500":"1500","1510":"1510","1410":"1410","1471":"1471","Donyford, St. Decuman's Parish, Somerset, England":"Somerset, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1410–1510":"1410–1510","1410–1500":"1410–1500","1471–1536":"1471–1536","1536":"1536","1500":"1500","1510":"1510","1410":"1410","1471":"1471","Donyford, St. Decuman's Parish, Somerset, England":"Somerset, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1410–1510":"1410–1510","1410–1500":"1410–1500","1471–1536":"1471–1536","1536":"1536","1500":"1500","1510":"1510","1410":"1410","1471":"1471","Donyford, St. Decuman's Parish, Somerset, England":"Somerset, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"John Waldron est né en 1410. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Elizabeth Waldron. Il est décédé en 1510, à l’âge de 100 ans."},"de":{"1410–1510":"1410–1510","1410–1500":"1410–1500","1471–1536":"1471–1536","1536":"1536","1500":"1500","1510":"1510","1410":"1410","1471":"1471","Donyford, St. Decuman's Parish, Somerset, England":"Somerset, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"John Waldron wurde 1410 geboren. Er hatte mit Elizabeth Waldron min